data.description:
REALTORS: Bring your buyers! Will pay 2% buyers agent fee

Picture perfect views of the Indian River from 35 feet of charming front deck.  Expansive impact resistant windows provide spectacular sunset scenery and clear rocket launches.  Newer roof in 2019, new impact windows, new a/c including ducts, new tankless water heater, new roof on air conditioned work shop with electric. 4 Large bedrooms plus a flex/office space. New custom designed kitchen with desirable quartz counter tops  and walk in pantry.  Spacious indoor laundry is oversized.  Luxury vinyl plank.  Parking spaces for 4 or  more vehicles.  Private, gated community park with boat ramp.  Hop and a skip to Cocoa Village
data.whatILove: Riding Bikes to Cocoa Village, the neighbors who walk by, the wildlife on the river. Amazing Community
